quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  6,125,to jis shakhs ko khuda chahta hai ke hadaayat bakhshay is ka seenah islam ke liye khol deta hai aur jisay chahta hai ke gumraah kere is ka seenah tang aur ghata howa kar deta hai goya woh aasman par charh raha hai is terhan khuda un logon par jo imaan nahi laatay azaab bhejta hai
  6,126,aur yahi tumahray perwar-digaar ka seedha rasta hai jo log ghhor karne walay hain un ke liye hum ne apni ayatain khol khol kar bayan kar di hain
  6,127,un ke liye un ke aamaal ke siilay mein perwar-digaar ke haan salamti ka ghar hai aur wohi un ka Dostdar hai
  6,128,aur jis din woh sab ( jin o ins ) ko jama kere ga ( aur farmaiye ga ke ) ae giroh jinnaat tum ne insanon se bohat ( faiday ) haasil kiye to jo insanon mein un ke Dostdar hon ge woh kahin ge ke perwar-digaar hum aik dosray se faida uthatay rahay aur ( aakhir ) is waqt ko poanch gay jo to ne hamaray liye muqarrarkiya tha khuda farmaiye ga ( ab ) tumhara thikana dozakh hai hamesha is mein ( jaltay ) raho ge magar jo khuda chahay be shak tumhara perwar-digaar Dana aur khabardaar hai
  6,129,aur isi terhan hum zaalmon ko un ke aamaal ke sabab jo woh karte they aik dosray par musallat kar dete hain
  6,130,ae junoo aur insanon ki jamaatkiya tumahray paas tum hi mein se paighambar nahi atay rahay jo meri ayatain tum ko parh parh kar sunaate aur is din ke samnay آموجود honay se darate they woh kahin ge ke ( perwar-digaar ) hamein apne gunaaho ka iqraar hai un logon ko dnyaki zindagi ne dhokay mein daal rakha tha aur ( ab ) khud apne oopar gawahi di ke kufar karte they
  6,131,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam! ) yeh ( jo paighambar atay rahay aur kitaaben nazil hoti rahen to ) is liye ke tumhara perwar-digaar aisa nahi ke bustiyon ko zulm se halaak kar day aur wahan ke rehne walon ko ( kuch bhi ) khabar nah ho
